   param  :  string (for FE_CHANGEVIEWMODE and FE_COMMAND), or nil

 #Returns:#
   result :  boolean

 #Description:#
   Except for its 1-st parameter, this function is identical to export.ProcessPanelEvent function
(see LuaFAR manual).


 ~User Modules~@UserModules@
 ~Contents~@Contents@

