 ~Contents~@Contents@

@ClosePanel
$^ #ClosePanel
 #ClosePanel(info, handle)#

 #Parameters:#
   info:   table ~tInfo~@tInfo@

 #Returns:#
   nothing

 #Description:#
   Except for its 1-st parameter, this function is identical to export.ClosePanel function
